copy something from the clipboard, navigate to the text, tap the 3 dots and 
there is the copy button. Compared to clipstack, open the app, navigate to 
the text you want to copy, tap the copy button, done. No 3 dots whatsoever. 
And if you want to merge, you dont need to tap many buttons, just pick the 
texts, long press it, and the merge button appears, tap it, and the texts 
get merged. With this app though, long press the texts, tap the 3 dots, do 
a little scroll, tap the merge button, then it will pop up a "delimiter" 
screen, tap ok, and they get merged. Wow! And this is a pro app!! Make

the point, straightforward, and save other unnecessary buttons in the 
settings or something. Also, please add a floating button, a tts button, a

and provide MUCH BETTER FEATURES AND INTERFACES than this one. And this one 
is a PRO version. How ironic.
